snippet.title: A Maze Dream - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Find the way to jump the fence. Play as a sheep solving puzzles with your cloud powers like freezeing, jump and move as a lightining through the end of the 45 aMAZEing stages. A fun journey for the dream gamers.

Wishlist now on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2397880/A_Maze_Dream_the_puzzle_journey/
